user.intro:
Studied Business Strategy / Computer Science because it was the quickest way to graduate, working full time as an APM at Salesforce based in SF.

I am diving deep into sustainability, climate, etc. so if you're interested then let's chat !!
user.lookingFor:
Build a network of founders! I hope to launch my own startup or join early stage companies in the climate space.

Also looking for anyone generally interested in sustainability.
